WhiteMoldSoybean dataset

Source: R/data-doc.R
WhiteMoldSoybean.Rd

National dataset of white mold severity and yield.

Usage

WhiteMoldSoybean

Format

A data frame with:

country

Country name

elevation

Field elevation

elevation_class

Elevation class

harvest_year

Year of harvest

inc

Incidence

inc_check

Check plot incidence

inc_class

Incidence class

location

Location name

region

Geographical region

scl

Soybean canopy layer

season

Crop season

state

State name

study

Study identifier

treat

Treatment applied

yld

Yield

yld_check

Yield of untreated check

yld_class

Yield class

Source

Del Ponte Lab internal data
